---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Personal Chefs — Client Testimonials That Fill Your Calendar | SocialProof" description="Personal chefs: collect client testimonials automatically and display them on your site. Build the social proof that turns inquiries into bookings. Free to start.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Personal Chefs
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Personal chef services live and die on referrals — but most clients search online before they reach out. SocialProof helps you capture glowing reviews from happy clients and display them exactly where new prospects are evaluating whether to book you.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The trust gap personal chefs face</h2>
      <p>Inviting a chef into your home is intimate. New clients aren't just buying a meal service — they're trusting you with their space, their dietary restrictions, their family's routines. That trust is hard to convey through a menu alone. Testimonials from current clients close that gap.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">A client saying "she accommodated my daughter's allergies without us even asking" or "I came home to a spotless kitchen and three days of incredible food" does more work than any bio you could write about yourself.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What converts new clients</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Dietary expertise:</strong> "Navigated my husband's keto and my vegetarian needs without complaint."</li>
        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> "Never once canceled. Always on time. Three years in and still going."</li>
        <li><strong>Clean & professional:</strong> "Left our kitchen cleaner than she found it every single time."</li>
        <li><strong>Flavor:</strong> "My kids ask for her food by name. We've replaced restaurant delivery entirely."</li>
        <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> "She remembered every preference without us having to repeat ourselves."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof fits your workflow</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>After a great meal or milestone</strong> (first month, anniversary of service), send the collection link.</li>
        <li><strong>Clients click one URL</strong> and write a few sentences — no account, no app, no friction.</li>
        <li><strong>You approve with one click.</strong> The testimonial appears on your website.</li>
        <li><strong>New prospects see it</strong> when they land on your site and decide whether to reach out.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Where to show testimonials as a personal chef</h2>
      <p>The highest-value placement: your <strong>services/pricing page</strong>. That's where interested prospects stall. A few strong testimonials right there answer the unspoken question: "Can I trust this person in my home?"</p>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Homepage — first impression counts</li>
        <li>Services page — right alongside your offering descriptions</li>
        <li>FAQ page — testimonials as social proof alongside your policies</li>
        <li>Inquiry/contact page — reduce hesitation at the booking moment</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Free forever for one widget</h2>
      <p>SocialProof's free plan gives you everything you need to start: collect testimonials via a shareable link, approve them, and embed a widget on your site. No credit card. No expiry. When you're ready to run multiple widgets or unlock advanced features, Pro is $9/month.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:3rem;padding:2rem;background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:8px;text-align:center;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:1rem;">Start collecting client testimonials today</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#000;color:#fff;padding:0.85rem 2rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;">Try SocialProof Free →</a>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#777;margin-top:0.75rem;">Free forever · No credit card required · 5-minute setup</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;" class="footer-links">
        <p>Also useful for: <a href="/for/caterers">Caterers</a> · <a href="/for/nutritionists">Nutritionists</a> · <a href="/for/freelancers">Freelancers</a> · <a href="/for/local-service">Local Service Businesses</a></p>
        <p>Compare tools: <a href="/vs/google-reviews">vs Google Reviews</a> · <a href="/vs/testimonial-io">vs Testimonial.io</a> · <a href="/vs/senja">vs Senja</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
